name: If I had a daughter, I would told her...
description:
If I had a daughter, I would told her Be bold.
I'm Roya, a 59 years old mother. I am very interested in NFTs. I have two sons but always liked to have a daughter, too. I love daughters! As everything has become virtual, my collection is my virtual daughter, it contains 10 virtual girls in 1/1 edition.
